{"tid":1323113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"6.21 夏日狂歡節 齊齊玩沙灘遊戲","createTime":"2019-07-16T06:46:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T07:19:12.000Z","uid":200042,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ed78ed2ffde0a3e0671ab97462976b79fed32380","tid":1323113,"uid":200042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:46:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">炎炎夏日將至，一眾市民都應投奔初夏，玩一眾港人愛玩的沙灘運動!!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">第一屆全民初夏運動會於金鐘舉行，屆時大家可帶備名種沙灘玩具，到場慶祝</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1. 飛碟</span><br />\n<br />\n受美國隊長同垃圾會君妖大隊長所啟發，大家可帶備飛碟，由於飛碟易於控制，加上價錢相宜，適合遠距離攻擊，而感覺亦比磚頭好，所以強烈建議<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2. 沙灘排球</span><br />\n<br />\n人妖打排球所描畫既殺波相信深入民心，希望一眾運動巴打帶排球於到時大大力殺落對家，強身健體<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">3. 浮棒</span><br />\n<br />\n大大支浮棒可臨場殺敵，軟身有助吸收攻擊，亦能遠距離對對家做成滋擾，顔色亦有助辨認自己人<br />\n<br />\n都係突然諗到，有建議大家可再講講"},{"pid":"196f3a792d46f72c5fd5875d162b30cf38a031cf","tid":1323113,"uid":200042,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:47:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aad29141b736b894542ffb8fb7f9ddfc7976785a","tid":1323113,"uid":200042,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:47:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"138fb73918939bb70c31c481e1d010d099d0f588","tid":1323113,"uid":200042,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:47:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"768e8c5240a5c5a3ce3571a6f89d1